# Environment Variables Example

Copy this to .env file in backend/ directory and fill in your values

## MongoDB
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/job_tracker
# For MongoDB Atlas: mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/job_tracker?retryWrites=true&w=majority

## Server
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

## JWT
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_key_change_this_in_production_to_random_string
JWT_EXPIRY=7d

## Optional: Frontend URL (for CORS)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
